{"tid":1685886,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"想各位盡量唔好扣帽子係記者身上","createTime":"2019-10-31T22:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T23:25:14.000Z","uid":318505,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"022fb91656b7622c2e131b557148c30f02732b58","tid":1685886,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T22:28:23.000Z","msg":"經歷左呢幾個月大家都對記者抱有敬意<br />\n相信係因為佢地堅守報導事實、挨得苦等嘅原因<br />\n但最近開始覺得大家當記者完全係自己人，<br />\n甚至扣啲唔應該扣嘅帽子去記者身上，<br />\n希望大家可以花少少時間諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解突然想打呢篇鳩post<br />\n事源係今晚立場有條片影到示威者鶳疑踩油撞人嘅呀叔<br />\n有人以為條片out fo係為左保護示威者<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yLTBOXT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyLTBOXT.png&h=8d235bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而事實係條片應該係校左auto，意外out fo<br />\n上圖為片段前半out fo，下圖為後半正常focus<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWsSnhR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWsSnhR.png&h=44b58638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UP2nKwd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUP2nKwd.png&h=de88c7e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亂咁扣帽子落記者身上，當正佢地係手足，對記者同手足其實都有影響<br />\n<br />\n記者：<br />\n- 前線記者會成為小器狗嘅針對對象<br />\n- 小器狗藍屍會造謠抹黑，減低媒體持平公信性<br />\n（唔洗同我講就算唔扣，藍狗都會揾位入記者，我都知）<br />\n<br />\n手足：<br />\n- 放低對鏡頭嘅戒心，覺得淨笠個口罩都可以出現鏡頭前<br />\n<br />\n眼瞓鳩打，仲有其他嘅自己諗。<br />\n呢個post並無以後要視記者為敵人嘅意思<br />\n只係覺得係記者履行職責嘅時候，作為讀者都要尊重翻<br />\n除左唔亂扣帽子，<br />\n最近睇live都覺得某啲嘢值得大家留意下：<br />\n避免係live緊個陣cm問直播員嘅個人嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n避免live時，真人主動r水吹（輕鬆場合就自行拿捏）<br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得上述問題雖然唔算經常發生<br />\n但都會偶爾出現<br />\n覺得啱嘅求各位幫p牌仔推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48886a8726925c350365f6a67bd75819e0160383","tid":1685886,"uid":320737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T22:29:49.000Z","msg":"豬撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5525eba3102979b393a2068d3ef31a8daa6dfd3","tid":1685886,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T22:31:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bab4bd22ae9113d0d92b8c508779ddf9a0c61cf6","tid":1685886,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5525eba3102979b393a2068d3ef31a8daa6dfd3","tid":1685886,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T22:31:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T22:33:23.000Z","msg":"點呀blocked user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人亂當記者係幫示威者咪叫扣帽子"},{"pid":"842adad513f2caf607c2661d01e41a5b6034d942","tid":1685886,"uid":266668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T22:41:38.000Z","msg":"啱 如果唔係又多樣野比班中立撚話"},{"pid":"ef14a9d4023e44bb5d391d9c0e1a46b84e27ba7a","tid":1685886,"uid":154634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:11:28.000Z","msg":"全世界傳媒都有立場架啦<br />\n係香港人咁on9覺得傳媒要「中立」<br />\n你估宜家黑警唔知自己做既野唔出得街？<br />\n傳媒「中立」就唔會發洩係記者朋友身上？<br />\n唔好on9 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79ab165a71bc218c2400f2ab7e35efce2a3269a","tid":1685886,"uid":145458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:22:13.000Z","msg":"出去發夢從來都係無視佢地"},{"pid":"5a56deeb4d02de69f8d3e75fa753e851b12d1d45","tid":1685886,"uid":280493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4K4xnXW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4K4xnXW.gif&h=dedb4388&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c687c72005f5929f4f769bd0c6a7e57232fb81f","tid":1685886,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef14a9d4023e44bb5d391d9c0e1a46b84e27ba7a","tid":1685886,"uid":154634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:11:28.000Z","msg":"全世界傳媒都有立場架啦<br />\n係香港